{
  "text": "Energy expenditure during nonswimming behaviors was based on the relationship between ODBA and oxygen consumption (V\u0307O 2 ) derived by [CITATION_1] V\u0307O 2 = 0.07 + 1.90 \u00d7 ODBA (r 2 = 0.71, p < 0.001, n = 21, Figure 2 ).",
  "correct_citation": {
